    <item>
      <title>Causation in Biology</title>
      <link>https://pierrickbourrat.github.io/project/causation/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 May 2021 22:05:20 +1000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://pierrickbourrat.github.io/project/causation/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Causation is at the heart of any scientific inquiry. I am interested in characterising this phenomenon both generally and more particularly in biological contexts. In particular, I have been interested in the concept of heritability, which is used in several subfields of biology. I have also developed several information theoretic measures of causation within the interventionist account and, more recently, proposed some ways to link information theory and the interventionist account to heritability.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
